OL,3,CEnergy price cap predicted to rise in
OL,4,CJanuary, raising household bills by 1%
OL,6,FCornwall Insight said: "Given the
OL,7,Fprice cap rise in October, many will
OL,8,Fhave been hoping to see a fall in the
OL,9,Fcap for January. Unfortunately,
OL,10,Fforecasts show that prices will be
OL,11,Fstaying relatively high for the
OL,12,Fremainder of winter."
OL,14,FDespite January's forecast increase,
OL,15,Fprices are still expected to fall
OL,16,Fslightly in both the second and fourth
OL,17,Fquarters of next year.
